Preface to the gentle reader - 1727 Edition
Finally is presented the Third Part of the Catena Aurea, which was
so desired and much sought by many people, and thus, the promise
made elsewhere is perfectly fulfilled. It would be a shame if one of

those beautiful and incomparable golden chains, just the noblest
