arcane. And if, according to the wishes of some people, this had
happened, this treatise might not have seen the light of day so that
their particular profits would not be interrupted. However, in
contemplating that the councils and secrets of kings and princes are
not to be mentioned, yet the works of the Almighty God, they are
gloriously praised and revealed, exalted as much above as in nature; in
